author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
There has been a lot of talk about Velvet Sundown over the past couple of weeks. I was trying to avoid it, but then I realised that their 'music' could actually serve a purpose - if you want to cut off your feelings. It's poor, but I liked the pictures - even if they're not from the "band's" official account. Who cares anyway because it's evidence that we've entered The Age of Fookin S***e.
